{"tid":1612601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有需要澄清］其實開槍果popo係想救同伴先拔槍","createTime":"2019-10-02T09:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T01:15:29.000Z","uid":115613,"like":4,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2d891042cf16aed04a6306d0a0a97cdf1863d800","tid":1612601,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-oksiH1zlsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-oksiH1zlsM&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=abc68b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-oksiH1zlsM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhsnvSP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhsnvSP.png&h=14bd36e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇事情要冷靜睇全面啲<br />\n以上片段睇到來龍去脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開槍果個係想衝去救人先拔槍<br />\n毒果果啲cut到popo開槍果角度<br />\n實在太以偏概全<br />\n<br />\n至於當時情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有沒時間同空間射向天/地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又有幾多反應時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />示威者用鐵棍攻擊有沒令槍走火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正須要獨立調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持成立獨調查委員會找出事情真相</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d3a65fe0bcd6a5b10d5cdf784145e100b5783a4","tid":1612601,"uid":230890,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2127c49317193beaa6258510eb34404526348cb","tid":1612601,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d3a65fe0bcd6a5b10d5cdf784145e100b5783a4","tid":1612601,"uid":230890,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已